{"tid":527770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街床蝨又嚟啦，精神崩潰","createTime":"2018-01-13T04:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T10:15:53.000Z","uid":7769,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fb3f01ddcfa16b0c5a546a8ff972b5bb5dd6d8","tid":527770,"uid":7769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"話說大半年前奶過一次野，搞左我成個幾月，<br />\n搵到佢地個竇係梳化底，於是立即掉左張梳化，<br />\n再喪噴DE粉，噴多個幾月先搞掂！<br />\n諗返起都覺得驚，訓訓下對腳feel到小小痕都會立即彈起身開電筒照，真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但估唔到事隔大半年（聽講佢地可以大半年唔活動都唔死）今日畀我係電視櫃前搵到隻細隻屍體，<br />\n我又即刻拆左個電視櫃睇但無乜發現，<br />\n所以噴左DE粉就算，各位請問有無其他心德可以分享下？<br />\n<br />\n唔想又長期精神緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617b9f738585e1d0af18962c580a8269344360a4","tid":527770,"uid":32577,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/125737_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F125737_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=8761fdae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/125741_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F125741_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=4bcd06a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea3f944ee697353b30dd65ebda3e6744e2810b6a","tid":527770,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"報復社會"},{"pid":"756faa8b645d59ecab65e58a5cd3b9bf30443d87","tid":527770,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:03:46.000Z","msg":"麥咁凍仲會有咩？你有冇比佢哋咬啊依家？"},{"pid":"33886e4c